<HEADLINE> Chinese Embassy in Kazakhstan Celebrates HK's Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALMA ATA, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese embassy in Kazakhstan
hosted a grand cocktail party here today, marking China's
resumption of the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong at
midnight Monday.
</P>
