<HEADLINE> Road Accident Kills 15 in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, July 1 (Xinhua) -- Fifteen people from a marriage
party were killed and 25 others injured when their van and a truck
collided head-on in Andhra Pradesh of southern India today.
</P>
<P>
Reports reaching here this evening said that 15 of the injured
were in serious condition. The accident happened when the
overloaded van lost its balance and hit the truck coming from the
opposite direction. The injured were rushed to hospital.  
</P>
</TEXT>
