<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese Embassy in Seychelles
today hosted a reception to celebrate the historic return of Hong
Kong to the motherland after 156 years of British colonial rule,
said reports reaching here from Victoria, capital of Seychelles.
</P>
