<HEADLINE> Serbian Economic Situation Improves </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, July 1 (Xinhua) -- The Republic of Serbia of the
Federal Republic of Yugoslavia has fulfilled its economic goal for
the first half of this year, Prime Minister Mirro Marjanovich said
today.
</P>
<P>
From January to June, Serbia's industrial production increased
by 7 percent compared with the same period last year, while
exports soared by 40 percent, the news agency Tunjug reported.
</P>
