<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, July 1 (Xinhua) -- A European special envoy said here
today that he is "very satisfied" with Albania's June 29 election
and the task ahead for the country is to harness its economy and
public order.
</P>
<P>
Franz Vranitzky, special envoy of the Organization for Security
and Cooperation in Europe (OSCE), made the conclusion after he had
