Chinese to settle the question of Taiwan in line with the basic
policy of peaceful reunification and 'one country, two systems'".
</P>
<P>
Yomiuri:
</P>
<P>
-- Japan's Administrative Reform Council has worked out a plan
to streamline government-controlled business, with the postal
services being privatized or changed into governemnt-operated
company.
</P>
<P>
